What is the result of calling `f(5)` in the following class?
```java
class Solver {
    static int r = 0;
    int f(int n) {
        if(n <= 0) return 1;
        if(n > 3) {
            r = n;
            return f(n-2) + 2;
        }
        return f(n-1) + r;
    }
}
```

